invoker.Command

  • Packages that use Command 
    Package Description
    invoker  

    • Uses of Command in invoker

      Classes in invoker that implement Command 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ComColler
      Class that represents the command Coller that paste the contents of the presse-papier (clipboard) into the buffer at the position of the initial cursor (cursor début).
      class  ComCopier
      Class that represents the command copier (copy) that copys the selected text in the buffer and pastes it in the presse-papier (clipboard).
      class  ComCouper
      Class that represents the command Couper (cut) that paste the selected text to the presse-papier (clipboard) and removes the selected text from the BufferZone.
      class  ComDecrDebut
      Class that represents the command décrementer début that decreses the initial cursor by one position.
      class  ComDecrFin
      Class that represents the command décrementer fin that decreses the final cursor by one position.
      class  ComEffacerApres
      Class that represents the command effacer Après that erases the following character to the initial cursor position.
      class  ComEffacerAvant
      Class that represents the command effacer Après that erases the following character to the initial cursor position.
      class  ComIncrDebut
      Class that represents the command incrémenter début that increases the initial cursor by one position
      class  ComIncrFin
      Class that represents the command incrémenter fin that increases the final cursor by one position
      class  ComInsererCaractere
      Class that represents the command inserer caracterere that that inserts a character received from the IHM and puts it into the buffer.
